name: Benjamin Sinclair
profile_summary: This 28-year-old man is a Software Engineer in the technology industry, currently living in Los Angeles, California, but originally from San Francisco, California. He's a graduate of the University of California, Los Angeles. Language-wise, he only speaks English. Lifelong learning, independence, and creativity are the values he cherishes the most. His interests range from hiking, to reading and gaming. A Capricorn, with an INTJ personality type, categorizes himself as agnostic and liberal in terms of religious beliefs and politics, respectively. He's currently looking for a serious long-term relationship, favoring monogamy. He is a straight white Caucasian who uses he/him/his pronouns. He has no children but is interested in having them in the future. He has a pet cat. He doesn't smoke, nor use marijuana or other drugs, but does drink occasionally. Being active, he exercises regularly.

She should be an active individual, standing within a height range of 5'3" to 6'1", who does not have children, but desires them in the future. The potential partner should be a straight non-smoker who enjoys drinking occasionally, and abstains from marijuana and other drugs. She would speak English and share values of independence, lifelong learning, and creativity.
